me n my unfinished mural in eva’s old place (aka my dream apartment n city sanctuary)
time rots away n leaves me wanting more of what now only lives on in my head. i miss this place n the memories in its walls. but everything feels brighter than that old era.
i’m appreciating the purity and light of this moment n excited for more paintings and murals on new walls.

i want to remember the taste of victory.
i want again to see the sweat and blood come out like a cleansing ritual. leeches and bloodletting of the middle ages. 
i want to listen to the same song over and over until music is only air waves that slide in n out my head.
i want to lose track of time so night becomes day and twilight wraps around and tucks me in and cradles me like an infant.
i want to forget my middle name.
i feel nothing and everything.
i’ll c u soon. hope you’ve been getting on ok.

(listening link in bio)

this album means so much to me and i sorta can’t believe it’s finally out in the world now.
it marks the beginning of a new chapter 🌟

I recorded it over the span of 3-4 years in the various bedrooms and places i’ve lived.
these songs are very dear to my heart . and when i listen to them i’m taken back to the specific period of my life when i wrote each one.

thanks everyone for supporting me all these years, especially those who’ve been here since i was 14 putting up music on soundcloud. i’ve come a long way since then, im excited for what’s to come .

thanks to @jaxonleft for doing the cover art n photos for this album.🌳
to @brianantonucci for mastering this chaotic project heheh🐦‍⬛
and to @avshatheawful for playing drums on “Wickerman”, lead guitar on “RolyPoly”, and bass on “Lingr”🖤

n thanks to all my friends n ppl out there who believe in me and my music and give it ur precious time and treat it with care 🎶 . i love you . ♥️
